snippet.title: Global Beta Trailer | VEILED EXPERTS
snippet.description:
VEILED EXPERTS™ is a Free-to-Play team-based online action shooter(TPS) developed by NEXON Games, Korea.

Pre-register now on Steam for prior access to the beta playtest
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1934780/VEILED_EXPERTS/

Check out the official website
https://global.vx.nexon.com/
